{"word":"G5586 - ψῆφος - psēphos - psay'-fos - Stone","slug":"G5586","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ψῆφος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>psēphos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>psay'-fos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Stone"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C8;&#x03B7;&#x0342;&#x03C6;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - pse&#x0304;phos</b> - <i>psay'-fos</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/G5584\">G5584</a>; a <i>pebble</i> (as worn smooth by <i>handling</i>), that is, (by implication of use as a <i>counter</i> or <i>ballot</i>) a <i>verdict</i> (of acquittal) or <i>ticket</i> (of admission); a <i>vote:</i> - stone, voice."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4785\">G4785</a>, <a href=\"#/G4860\">G4860</a>, <a href=\"#/G5585\">G5585</a>"}]}